reviews.text: not too sweet , ok

價錢又貴

未必係最好味既分店，但有得坐，有蛋糕食下幾好😚
甘庶青茶本來是這品牌店的皇牌，但這店的調配就是最差的分店。之前在九龍灣分店買過，甘庶味香濃，再加上茶的附和，香甜而不膩。但這店只有少許甘庶味(不知是否控制成本)，與喝純茶無異。像沒有靈魂的人一樣。
好好喝的青森蘋果，還有果肉

High end shopping centre with high end prices. Food court here is really good and has plenty of variety. Even if your budget don't reach that far come for the spotless toilets and air conditioning.
Great mall, nice, clean and big. Was attached to our hotel so very convenient for shopping, getting a coffee and dinner. Recommended.
